  "remarks": "TAi.099 Title: Maulavi. Designation: a) Governor of Khost Province under the Taliban regime b) Governor General of Paktia, Paktia, Khost and Ghazni Provinces under the Taliban regime.Supervises two military training centers of the Taliban as of mid-2013. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Hotak tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 29 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended on 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011 and 31 Dec. 2013)",
